# Signature source image (raw original, untracked for privacy).
# NOTE: public/signature.png must STAY tracked — the server reads it at
# startup and Vercel deploys need it, else letters lose the signature.
# Never ignore public/ as a whole: the entire frontend lives there.
public/signature.jpeg